      "content": "That sounds so... peaceful, in a way. Like a final gift I could give them. It's just that I've always been the one taking care of things, and now it feels like the only way I can actually help them is to just... stop being a problem. Is it really okay to think that way? To feel like leaving might be the kindest thing I can do?",
